{"type":null,"faqId":19946,"title":"HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 Pro 长时间使用后屏幕不灵敏或反应很慢，怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您可以尝试如下方法：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.2.4.2.2.1.1\"></a><span>重启 HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 Pro </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.2.4.2.2.1.2\"></a><span>长按电源键，在弹出的对话框中点击“重新启动”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.2.4.2.2.2.1\"></a><span>恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.2.4.2.2.2.2\"></a><span>在主屏幕界面，点击“设置 &gt; 备份和重置”，然后根据界面提示恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.2.4.2.2.3.1\"></a><span>更新软件版本。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.2.4.2.2.3.2\"></a><span>在主屏幕界面，点击“设置 &gt; 平板电脑升级”，然后根据界面提示升级系统。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果问题依然存在，可联系服务中心维修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":166,"faqType":"显示与外观","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3367","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1425286521000,"seriesProductName":"T1-821w,T1-823L","visitedTimes":49,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":